marketCapHint: Market capitalization of the token in circulation. Market cap = current price * circulating supply
onChainVolumeHint: Volume of coin transfers and swaps
liquidityHint: Total volume of two tokens in the liquidity pool
dexVolumeHint: Coin trading volume on DEX exchanges
dexTradersHint: Number of traders who buy or sell this coin on DEX exchanges
circSupplyHint: The number of coins circulating on the market and in public hands. Circulating supply = Total supply - locked coins that cannot influence the supply of the coin on the market
